title: Frank Sinatra - Sinatra And Swingin' Brass (2014) [24-96 HD FLAC
description:
Frank Sinatra's debut recording with arranger and composer Neal Hefti, this album is mainly comprised of re-recordings of songs Sinatra had released earlier in his career with a different record label. All the great songwriters are represented here: Porter, Gershwin, Ellington and Mercer, while Sinatra himself is in fine vocal form. Among the musicians backing Sinatra are Ben Webster on tenor saxophone and Conte Candoli on trumpet. (publisher notes)
